buildCommand: cd ../.. && echo "node: $(node -v)" && echo "pnpm: $(pnpm -v)" && pnpm turbo run build --filter=verifactu-landing
installCommand: cd ../.. && echo "node: $(node -v)" && echo "corepack: $(corepack --version)" && corepack enable && corepack prepare pnpm@10.27.0 --activate && echo "pnpm: $(pnpm -v)" && pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
